<section id="ec">
  <title>ec</title>
  <para>End of a spanning original code.</para>
  <para><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>.</para>
  <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>
  <simplelist><?oxy_custom_end?>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="0,255,0"?>
    <member>This is object atomic, yet it is used to close spans.<?oxy_custom_end?></member>
  </simplelist>
  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis></para>
  <simplelist>
    <member><olink targetdoc="structural/source.xml" targetptr="source"><code>source</code></olink>
      array and <olink targetdoc="structural/target.xml" targetptr="target"
        ><code>target</code></olink> array.</member>
  </simplelist>
  <para><emphasis>Properties:</emphasis></para>
  <simplelist>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"kind"</code>, a
        <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/kind.xml" targetptr="kind"><code>kind</code></olink>
      string with fixed value <code>"ec"</code>,
      <glossterm>required</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"canCopy"</code>.
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/cancopy.xml" targetptr="cancopy"
        ><code>canCopy</code></olink> string with value <code>"yes"</code> or <code>"no"</code>,
        <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"canDelete"</code>,
        a<olink targetdoc="../../attributes/candelete.xml" targetptr="cancopy"
          ><code>canDelete</code></olink> string with value <code>"yes"</code> or <code>"no"</code>,
        <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"canOverlap"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/canoverlap.xml" targetptr="canoverlap"
          ><code>canOverlap</code></olink> string with value <code>"yes"</code> or
      <code>"no"</code>, <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"canReorder"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/canreorder.xml" targetptr="canreorder"
          ><code>canReorder</code></olink> string with value <code>"yes"</code>, <code>"no"</code>,
      or <code>"firstNo"</code>, <glossterm>optional</glossterm> with default value
        <code>"yes"</code><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"copyOf"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/copyof.xml" targetptr="copyof"
        ><code>copyOf</code></olink> string with NMTOKEN value,
      <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"dataRef"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/dataref.xml" targetptr="dataref"
        ><code>dataRef</code></olink> string with NMTOKEN value,
      <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member><!-- pending discussion with Fredrik -->-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"dir"</code>, a
        <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/dir.xml" targetptr="dir"><code>dir</code></olink> string
      with value <code>"ltr"</code>, <code>"rtl"</code>, or <code>"auto"</code>,
        <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"disp"</code>, a
        <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/disp.xml" targetptr="disp"><code>disp</code></olink>
      string, <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"equiv"</code>, a
        <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/equiv.xml" targetptr="equiv"><code>equiv</code></olink>
      string, <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
      <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"id"</code>, a
        <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/id.xml" targetptr="id"><code>id</code></olink> string
      with NMTOKEN value, <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"isolated"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/isolated.xml" targetptr="isolated"
        ><code>isolated</code></olink> string with value <code>"yes"</code> or <code>"no"</code>,
        <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"startRef"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/startref.xml" targetptr="startref"
        ><code>startRef</code></olink> string with NMTOKEN value,<?oxy_custom_end?>
      <glossterm><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,198,140"?>required<?oxy_custom_end?></glossterm></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"subFlows"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/subflows.xml" targetptr="subflows"
        ><code>subFlows</code></olink> string,
      <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"subType"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/subtype.xml" targetptr="subtype"
        ><code>subType</code></olink> string,
      <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <member>-
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"codeType"</code>,
      a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/codeType.xml" targetptr="codeType"
        ><code>codeType</code></olink> string with value <code>"fmt"</code>, <code>"ui"</code>,
        <code>"quote"</code>, <code>"link"</code>, <code>"image"</code>, <code>"its:generic"</code>,
      or <code>"other"</code>, <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>
    <member>- attributes from other namespaces,
      <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
  </simplelist>
  <para><emphasis>Example:</emphasis></para>
  <programlisting><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>
&lt;unit id="1"&gt;
  &lt;originalData&gt;
    &lt;data id="d1"&gt;\b &lt;/data&gt;
    &lt;data id="d2"&gt;\i &lt;/data&gt;
    &lt;data id="d3"&gt;\b0 &lt;/data&gt;
    &lt;data id="d4"&gt;\i0 &lt;/data&gt;
  &lt;/originalData&gt;
  &lt;segment&gt;
    &lt;source&gt;Text in &lt;sc id="1" dataRef="d1"/&gt;bold &lt;sc id="2"
        dataRef="d2"/&gt; and&lt;ec startRef="1" dataRef="d3"/&gt;
         italics&lt;ec startRef="2" dataRef="d4"/&gt;. &lt;/source&gt;
  &lt;/segment&gt;
&lt;/unit&gt;
<?oxy_custom_end?><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?>

{
  "id": "1",
  "kind": "unit",
  "originalData": {
    "d1": "\\b ",
    "d2": "\\i ",
    "d3": "\\b0 ",
    "d4": "\\i0 "
  },
  "subunits": [
    {
      "kind": "segment",
      "source": [
        { "text": "Text in " },
        { "id": "1", "kind": "sc" },
        { "text": "bold" },
        { "id": "2", "kind": "sc" },
        { "text": "<?oxy_custom_end?><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>\n<?oxy_custom_end?><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?>and" },
        { "dataRef": "d3", "kind": "ec", "startRef": "1" },
        { "text": " italics" },
        { "dataRef": "d4", "kind": "ec", "startRef": "2" },
        { "text": ". " }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

<?oxy_custom_end?>
</programlisting>
  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Constraints</title>
    <listitem>
      <para>The following <firstterm>JLIFF Module</firstterm>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>properties<?oxy_custom_end?>
        are
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>explicitly<?oxy_custom_end?>
        allowed <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>by the wildcard
          <code>other</code><?oxy_custom_end?>:</para>
      <para>
        <simplelist>
          <member>-
              <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"fs_fs"</code>,
            a <olink targetdoc="../attributes/fs.xml" targetptr="fs"><code>fs_fs</code></olink>
            string<?oxy_custom_end?>, provided that the Constraints specified in the <olink
              targetdoc="modules/fs/fs.xml" targetptr="fs-mod">Format Style Module</olink> are
            met.</member>
          <member>-
              <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"fs_subFs"</code>,
            a <olink targetdoc="../attributes/subfs.xml" targetptr="subfs"
              ><code>fs_subFs</code></olink> string,<?oxy_custom_end?> provided that the Constraints
            specified in the <olink targetdoc="modules/fs/fs.xml" targetptr="fs-mod">Format Style
              Module</olink> are met.</member>
          <member>-
              <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"slr_equivStorage"</code>,
            a <olink targetdoc="../attributes/size_restriction/equiv-storage.xml"
              targetptr="equiv-storage"><code>slr_equivStorage</code></olink><?oxy_custom_end?>
            object, provided that the Constraints specified in the <olink
              targetdoc="modules/size_restriction/specification.xml"
              targetptr="size_restriction_module">Size and Length Restriction Module</olink> are
            met.</member>
          <member>-
              <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"slr_sizeInfo"</code>,
            a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/size_restriction/size-info.xml"
              targetptr="slr_sizeInfo"><code>slr_sizeInfo</code></olink> string, provided that the
            Constraints specified in the <olink
              targetdoc="modules/size_restriction/specification.xml"
              targetptr="size_restriction_module">Size and Length Restriction Module</olink> are
            met.<?oxy_custom_end?></member>
          <member>-
              <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"slr_sizeInfoRef"</code>,
            a <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/size_restriction/size-info-ref.xml"
              targetptr="slr_sizeInfoRef"><code>slr_sizeInfoRef</code></olink> string, provided that
            the Constraints specified in the <olink
              targetdoc="modules/size_restriction/specification.xml"
              targetptr="size_restriction_module">Size and Length Restriction Module</olink> are
            met.<?oxy_custom_end?></member>
        </simplelist>
      </para>
      <simplelist>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>
        <member>- attributes from the namespace <code>urn:oasis:names:tc:xliff:fs:2.0</code>,
            <glossterm>optional</glossterm>, provided that the Constraints specified in the <olink
            targetdoc="modules/fs/fs.xml" targetptr="fs-mod">Format Style Module</olink> are
          met.</member>
        <member>- attributes from the namespace
            <code>urn:oasis:names:tc:xliff:sizerestriction:2.0</code>,
            <glossterm>optional</glossterm>, provided that the Constraints specified in the <olink
            targetdoc="modules/size_restriction/specification.xml"
            targetptr="size_restriction_module">Size and Length Restriction Module</olink> are
          met.<?oxy_custom_end?></member>
        <!-- may need to allow ITSM at a later stage, but not needed by now 7th Aug, 2015. -->
      </simplelist>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>No other <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>properties<?oxy_custom_end?>
        <glossterm>must</glossterm> be used.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>The values of the properties <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/cancopy.xml"
          targetptr="cancopy"><code>canCopy</code></olink>, <olink
          targetdoc="../../attributes/candelete.xml" targetptr="candelete"
          ><code>canDelete</code></olink> and <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/canoverlap.xml"
          targetptr="canoverlap"><code>canOverlap</code></olink>
        <glossterm>must</glossterm> be the same as the values the ones in the <olink
          targetdoc="../inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"><code>sc</code></olink> element corresponding
        to this end code.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>The value of the property <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/canreorder.xml"
          targetptr="canreorder"><code>canReorder</code></olink>
        <glossterm>must</glossterm> be <code>"no"</code> if the value of <olink
          targetdoc="../../attributes/canreorder.xml" targetptr="canreorder"
          ><code>canReorder</code></olink> is <code>"firstNo"</code> in the <olink
          targetdoc="../inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"><code>sc</code></olink> element corresponding
        to this end code.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>The property <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/isolated.xml" targetptr="isolated"
            ><code>isolated</code></olink>
        <glossterm>must</glossterm> be set to <code>"yes"</code> if and only if the <olink
          targetdoc="../inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"><code>sc</code></olink> element corresponding
        to this end code is not in the same <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/unit.xml"
          targetptr="unit"><code>unit</code></olink> and set to <code>"no"</code> otherwise.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem id="ecIFF">
      <para>If and only if the property <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/isolated.xml"
          targetptr="isolated"><code>isolated</code></olink> is set to <code>"yes"</code>, the
        property <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/id.xml" targetptr="id"><code>id</code></olink>
        <glossterm>must</glossterm> be used instead of the property <olink
          targetdoc="../../attributes/startref.xml" targetptr="startref"
          ><code>startRef</code></olink> that <glossterm>must</glossterm> be used otherwise.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para><!-- pending discussion with Fredrik --> If and only if the property <olink
          targetdoc="../../attributes/isolated.xml" targetptr="isolated"
          ><code>isolated</code></olink> is set to <code>"yes"</code>, the property <olink
          targetdoc="../../attributes/dir.xml" targetptr="dir"><code>dir</code></olink>
        <glossterm>may</glossterm> be used, otherwise the property <olink
          targetdoc="../../attributes/dir.xml" targetptr="dir"><code>dir</code></olink>
        <glossterm>must not</glossterm> be used on the <link linkend="ec"><code>ec</code></link>
        element. </para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Processing Requirements</title>
    <listitem>
      <para><firstterm>Extractors</firstterm>
        <glossterm>must not</glossterm> use the <olink targetdoc="../inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"
            ><code>sc</code></olink> / <olink targetdoc="../inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec"
            ><code>ec</code></olink> pair to represent standalone codes.</para>
      <para>Rationale: Using a spanning code for a standalone code can easily result in having text
        inside a span where the original format does not allow it.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
